1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Ever wondered why AI sometimes makes things up?

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:08,800
AI language models predict what words should come next, based on patterns in data.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,600
But they’re not programmed to verify truth.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,200
They generate what's plausible.

5
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:17,200
This leads to 'hallucinations' — confident statements that aren’t accurate.

6
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:22,400
Understanding this helps us use AI more wisely, knowing it’s not always reliable.

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,800
Want to learn more about AI?

